      <title>
        Jerry Jones Told Players to Stand for the Anthem or They Would Be Off the Team
      </title>
      <link>https://www.factopolis.com/person/greg-abbott/2017-08-01/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.factopolis.com/person/greg-abbott/2017-08-01/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <blockquote>
          Thank you Jerry Jones: Cowboys Jerry Jones to Players: Stand for the Anthem or you&rsquo;re off team <a href="https://twitter.com/NFL">@NFL</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/dallascowboys">@dallascowboys</a>
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          <cite>â€” Greg Abbott, Twitter</cite>
